high_descs: Take a step to your right.
Pick up the pan on the front left burner.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on your right and turn right to face it when you get there.
Chill the pan in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter that's to the right of the toaster then turn left to face it when you get there.
Put the pan on the counter to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the counter.

high_descs: Move a bit to the right to face the front of the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front left burner.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on the right.
Place the pan inside of the fridge, close the door, open the door, take the pan out, close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the pan down to the right of the toaster on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To chill a pan and put it on the counter.

high_descs: Move a step to your right to stand in front of the stove.
Pick up the pan from the front left burner of the stove.
Turn left to carry the pan to the fridge.
Place the pan on the second shelf in the fridge, close the door, and then remove after a few seconds.
Turn right and carry the pan to the counter space between the toaster and stove.
Place the pan on the counter to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold pan on the counter by the toaster.
